        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            I’m a musician, coder, and robotics enthusiast who loves creating things that merge 
            creativity with technology. I’ve produced and released original music, handled 
            recording and mixing, and developed a detailed ear that pushes me to refine my craft. 
            My curiosity also drives my coding work, where I’ve taught myself Python and machine 
            learning through hands-on projects. I enjoy exploring problems deeply, iterating, and 
            building better tools—whether in a studio, on a robotics field, or behind a keyboard.
        </p>
