    <!-- PROJECTS -->
    <section class="section" id="projects">
        <h2>Projects</h2>

        <!-- Harmoniq -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">Harmoniq — AI-Powered Music-Creation Studio</div>
            <p>
                Developed as a first-year innovation project at the USC Iovine & Young Academy, 
                Harmoniq is an AI-driven platform that transforms raw vocal recordings into polished, 
                release-ready tracks. It addresses the complexity and high cost of traditional 
                music-production tools while offering intuitive features such as real-time mastering 
                feedback, genre-aware processing, personalized sound profiles, A/B comparisons, 
                and transparent AI explanations.
            </p>
            <p>
                The project included market analysis, a competitive landscape study, financial projections, 
                and a freemium-based business model. I helped shape the concept, design features, and 
                articulate the product vision as part of a collaborative multidisciplinary team.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Hit Analyzer -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">AI “Hit Potential” Analyzer</div>
            <p>
                A machine learning tool that identifies patterns across decades of songs to predict 
                whether a new track might succeed commercially. Built the dataset, model, and 
                testing pipeline from scratch.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Album Project -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">Produced & Released Album</div>
            <p>
                Produced, recorded, mixed, and mastered a 27-minute, fully original band album. 
                Managed nearly every instrument and perfected details through continuous iteration. 
                Reached over 8,000 streams.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Robotics -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">Robotics Team Leadership</div>
            <p>
                Captain and lead coder for the Sidwell Friends Robotics Team. Competed in major 
                regional and state tournaments and helped the team earn multiple top-four finishes, 
                including a first-place victory in the MATE competition.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Breakout Mentors -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">Independent Python & ML Project</div>
            <p>
                Advanced Python and machine learning practice through Breakout Mentors. Built 
                creative programs including music-analysis tools based on algorithms and data patterns.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Community Power -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">AI Training Chatbot – Community Power</div>
            <p>
                Created an AI chatbot designed to simulate conversations between landowners and 
                companies to help train employees in communication.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Ingenuity Prep -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">Ingenuity Prep Robotics Program (Founder)</div>
            <p>
                Launched and taught a weekly robotics program at an under-resourced elementary 
                school. Designed custom lessons and hands-on activities.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Georgetown Internship -->
        <div class="project">
            <div class="project-title">Leadership Initiatives – Georgetown Internship</div>
            <p>
                Worked with business and development experts to improve a small organization’s 
                marketing and infrastructure. Co-led the project team and helped secure grant funding.
            </p>
